<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-8">
        <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

            <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 16 April 2025</p>
            <p><strong>ANZ Havyaka Team</strong> is dedicated to protecting the privacy of our community members. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect your personal information when you use our website. By using our website, you agree to the practices described in this policy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6">
            <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg mb-6 p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
                    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, contact information, etc., provided by you when you join the community directory or communicate with us.</li>
                    <li><strong>Non-Personal Information:</strong> IP address, browser type, device information, browsing activity, etc., collected automatically through cookies and analytics tools.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg mb-6 p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
                    <li>To provide and improve our website and community services.</li>
                    <li>To manage the community directory and enhance the user experience.</li>
                    <li>To communicate with you and respond to your inquiries.</li>
                    <li>To comply with legal obligations and protect our rights.</li>
                    <li>To comply with relevant privacy laws and regulations applicable to users in Australia and New Zealand.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg mb-6 p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">3. Information Sharing & Disclosure</h2>
                <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. However, we may share information with:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
                    <li>Community members.</li>
                    <li>Service providers assisting in website operation and maintenance.</li>
                    <li>Legal authorities if required by law or to protect our legal rights.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg mb-6 p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">4. Data Security</h2>
                <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, loss, misuse, or alteration. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg mb-6 p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">5. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
                <p>We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance user experience and analyze usage. You can control or disable cookies through your browser settings.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg mb-6 p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">6. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have rights regarding your personal information, including access, correction, deletion, and restriction of processing. This includes rights under the Privacy Act 1988 (Australia) and the Privacy Act 2020 (New Zealand). Contact us to exercise these rights.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg mb-6 p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">7. Community Directory</h2>
                <p>If you choose to be listed in the community directory, your provided information will be displayed as intended. Please review your entries before submitting them.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg mb-6 p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg mb-6 p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">9. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [Insert Contact Information].</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
